sentences.english: I was gratified at the attendance to my talk, and the enthusiastic response.
sentences.chinese: 聽衆對我的發言予以熱烈的響應，令我深感榮幸。

sentences.english: It gives me great pleasure to introduce Dr.Robert Dundee, who will be with us for two years.
sentences.chinese: 我很榮幸介紹羅伯，丹迪博士，他將與我們共事兩年。

sentences.english: We are delighted to be working with a company of such high standing.
sentences.chinese: 我們很榮幸能與一家名譽如此之高的雄司合作。

sentences.english: It's my honor to make prelude for the collected essays.
sentences.chinese: 如今能爲這本散文集作序，我覺得很榮幸。

sentences.english: I am honored this year was selected as the flag raisers.
sentences.chinese: 我，今年很榮幸的被選爲升旗手。

sentences.english: I am honoured to have had the opportunity to see a Lynx up close and personal.
sentences.chinese: 可是我很榮幸地能夠有機會近距離看到這個猞猁。

sentences.english: Charmed to see you, Mr. Redond.
sentences.chinese: 雷德蒙先生，見到您很榮幸。

sentences.english: C:It's a privilege to know you, Mr. McNiel.
sentences.chinese: 很榮幸能認識你，麥克尼爾先生。

sentences.english: I feel deeply honored to be playing against the former Wimbledon Champion.
sentences.chinese: 能與溫布爾登前冠軍球手比賽，我深感榮幸。

sentences.english: I had only the credit of servilely copying such sentences as I was ashamed to put my name to .
sentences.chinese: 我只是榮幸地恭錄那些我羞於爲之署名的語句。

sentences.english: It is our honour that you can come to our class for learning communication.
sentences.chinese: 很榮幸你們能來我們班進行學習交流。

sentences.english: Meade instruments has been a proud partner of Jinghua and Hejian for 15 years.
sentences.chinese: 米德器械很榮幸與晶華和赫建做了15年的合作伙伴。

sentences.english: Woa,I'm really honoured you went through all this trouble just for my sake.
sentences.chinese: 喔，我很榮幸你經歷了這麼多困難僅僅是因爲我。

sentences.english: I'm honored, but I'm not sure I'm the right person.
sentences.chinese: 很榮幸，不過我是否勝任，可沒把握。

sentences.english: And I am honored to serve as the hand of your will in Alterac.
sentences.chinese: 我很榮幸可以在奧特蘭克擔任您的助手。

sentences.english: It's my pleasure to stand here and give all of you a speech concetrate on the English name of our country.
sentences.chinese: 我很榮幸站在這裏發表聚焦我們祖國英文名的演講。

to be willing to do sth/to be ready to do sth/to be happy to do sth/content/satisfied
